  "text": "The method is similar to [CITATION_1] , Lemma 9.13, which deals with the case when k is a number field and (k i ) is the family of its completions for miscellaneous A, like A = π 1 (X) or A = π ab 1 (X). For the convenience of the reader we give a grouptheoretic version of the argument.",
